These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, french, pakistani, italian
1. the french is in an odd position##4
2. the italian is between the australian and the french##2
3. the italian is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | australian | italian | french | pakistani |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: pepper, lettuce, lime, raspberry
1. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
2. the person eating lettuce is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the person eating pepper##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | lettuce | pepper | raspberry | lime |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, romance, adventure, comedy
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
2. the person watching horror movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching adventure movies is between the person watching comedy movies and the person watching romance movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | comedy | adventure | romance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, parkour, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
2. the person who's sport is parkour is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's sport is parkour##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Sport   | basketball | badminton | lacrosse | parkour |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
