1. the person who's sport is golf is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | baseball | golf | weightlifting | badminton |

