1. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
2. the fan of classical is between the fan of trance and the fan of indie##2
3. the fan of classical is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |  3  |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | trance | classical | indie |

