2. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Hobby   | puzzles | dancing | camping | rock-climbing |

