.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-11::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, western, scientific, crime
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
2. the person watching western movies is in an even position##4
3. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person watching scientific movies and the person watching crime movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | fantasy | scientific | western |

