.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-12::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, taxi, tram, car
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person driving the taxi is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |  3  |    4    |
| Transport   | tram | taxi | car | helicopter |

