1. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking mirinda and the person drinking tea##2
3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2     |  3   |   4   |
| Beverage   | mirinda | 7up | tea | iced-tea |

