.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, firefighter, lawyer, musician
1. the lawyer is in an odd position##4
2. the musician is on the left of the lawyer##1
3. the lawyer is on the left or right of the firefighter##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Job   | electrician | musician | lawyer | firefighter |

 